HEADWORD: Phacops
<hw>Pha"cops</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr.
<grk>fako`s</grk> a lentil + <grk>'w`ps</grk>, <grk>'wpo`s</grk>, the
eye.]</ety> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>A genus of trilobites found in the
